      <profileDesc>
         <abstract>
            <p>The miracle of a criminal, whose mother had entrusted him to Mary and who was saved from execution by her 
                  intercessions, exists in many versions, whose relations are not well studied. This record refers to the version translated in
                  <bibl>
                  <ptr target="bm:Budge1923Miracles"/>
                  <citedRange unit="item">31</citedRange>
               </bibl>.  Another version translated by Budge is <ref type="work" corresp="LIT3616Miracle"/>. It is likely that more versions could be differentiated.
                  The general ID
                  to be used in cases were the precise version cannot be identified is 
                  <ref type="work" corresp="LIT3692Miracle"/>. </p>
         </abstract>
